    "description": "忘掉你所知道的有关漂移的一切。《惯性漂移》的游戏场景设定在 90 年代的复古未来，这款街机赛车竞速游戏有着破坏性的独特操控模式，完美实现双摇杆漂移力学。《惯性漂移》提供全新的无障碍环境和街机竞速挑战类型 — 为玩家带来前所未有的驾驶体验。<br><br><br>&quot;独一无二的双摇杆控制，助您完成精确漂移 — 右手摇杆让玩家实现对漂移动作的完全控制。为新玩家带来奇妙的直觉体验，满足游戏高手的独特挑战需求。<br><br><strong>16 辆带有强烈个人风格的赛车</strong> — 每辆赛车都像一头拥有个性十足的野兽，等待着你的驯服。赶快坐进驾驶座，尝试驯服掀背运动车，轿跑车，超级跑车等各种车型！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1184480/extras/a50221607577ec58ab12e60479ef0c97.poster.avif?t=1737474820\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1184480/extras/a50221607577ec58ab12e60479ef0c97.webm?t=1737474820\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1184480/extras/a50221607577ec58ab12e60479ef0c97.mp4?t=1737474820\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br> <br><strong>20 条要求超高的赛道</strong> — 撕开霓虹灯下的城市街道，在乡村寺庙建筑群周围狂奔，迎头冲下蜿蜒的山路。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1184480/extras/3a51428c215a1c1f638a00ee62c89420.poster.avif?t=1737474820\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1184480/extras/3a51428c215a1c1f638a00ee62c89420.webm?t=1737474820\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1184480/extras/3a51428c215a1c1f638a00ee62c89420.mp4?t=1737474820\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong> 90 年代的复古未来风游戏场景</strong> — 设定在霓虹粉色日落和暮色天空下夸张而奇特的环境之中。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1184480/extras/d9088cffc53a3ababe2d1bbcaf6d734c.poster.avif?t=1737474820\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1184480/extras/d9088cffc53a3ababe2d1bbcaf6d734c.webm?t=1737474820\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1184480/extras/d9088cffc53a3ababe2d1bbcaf6d734c.mp4?t=1737474820\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>单人故事模式</strong> — 通过组合竞速，一对一单挑，计时赛和风格对决来完善你的驾驶技巧！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1184480/extras/913b52a7bd3696e8f6fb25d045c4acf5.poster.avif?t=1737474820\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1184480/extras/913b52a7bd3696e8f6fb25d045c4acf5.webm?t=1737474820\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1184480/extras/913b52a7bd3696e8f6fb25d045c4acf5.mp4?t=1737474820\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>本地和在线多人游戏 — 认为自己已经掌握了完美的漂移技术吗？这就是你证明自己的最佳方式。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1184480/extras/6715d8992d7dea202e9a988e92f004d7.poster.avif?t=1737474820\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1184480/extras/6715d8992d7dea202e9a988e92f004d7.webm?t=1737474820\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1184480/extras/6715d8992d7dea202e9a988e92f004d7.mp4?t=1737474820\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
